Quizy is a quiz framework written on top of the authentication framework - phpUserAuth
(http://iambot.net/projects/phpuserauth/). Writing a mini quiz framework on top of the
authentication framework itself makes it very secure.

Author: Sibi
E-mail: sibi@psibi.in
License: GNU GPLv3

Installation
-------------

1) The module consists of two parts - Authentication framework and the quiz part. Initially
   install the authentication framework. For instructions regarding it, go to the location
   ./quiz/user/readme.
2) For installing the quiz module, execute two sql script named results.sql and questions.sql
   under the directory script. Make sure that the database under which the sql should be executed
   should be the same as that of which was followed on step 1.

